      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification for selection of turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive law, with sensitivity analysis demonstrating robustness to model form assumptions at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected without documented sensitivity comparison against alternative turbulence closures. The power-law hemolysis model was adopted from literature without re-calibration to pump-specific shear histories. Model form uncertainty is not quantified — not assessed."
    },
